		title: "Aluminium"
		icon: {id: "gtceu:aluminium_ingot", Count: 1b}
		description: ["Aluminium ore is abundant but useless without the EBF — it requires 1700K to smelt, far above what a furnace can provide. Run Bauxite ore through the Macerator for dust, then smelt the dust in the EBF.", "Aluminium Plates are the main material in MV Machine Hulls. You'll need a lot of them. Set up a dedicated EBF line for aluminium and don't stop feeding it."]
