		description: ["MV unlocks the Electrolyzer, the Chemical Reactor, the Large Boiler, and the Industrial Centrifuge — machines that process materials GregTech couldn't touch at LV. The Electrolyzer decomposes compounds into elements. The Chemical Reactor synthesizes them back.", "Build at least one Electrolyzer and one Chemical Reactor. The recipes they unlock are the backbone of HV prep."]
